{"tid":285134,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得畢業後搵到工但又少左自由個心情好矛盾？","createTime":"2017-06-15T13:52:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-16T19:28:47.000Z","uid":31531,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ecd91c789b186ef7b43df6630b5c1520ffc4adce","tid":285134,"uid":31531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T13:52:31.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我係今年畢業生，依家準備做老師<br />\n搵到工係開心，因為有收入<br />\n可以買到自己想買既野，去旅行等等<br />\n但同一時間諗諗下我失去左以前做學生時候既自由<br />\n由於我男朋友仲讀緊書<br />\n一諗到第時我少左時間可以見到佢，陪到佢，甚至等佢放學，就覺得好sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講真，我好驚第時因爲少左時間見<br />\n一個返工一個返學<br />\n好驚會出現左個差距，好驚唔再好似依家咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唉，個心情好矛盾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔洗講咩分手，因為我唔會，我好愛我男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25c66bdcf48e74a065ca232a1f6d6f5d60ae60c3","tid":285134,"uid":31531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T13:54:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"79e615d7a3c6f8c11097f3090c310fe6c8d97785","tid":285134,"uid":31531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T13:56:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5f9e378036a040abb35dc61de6328ca4490598e4","tid":285134,"uid":24570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T14:20:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a4e4927ade11095e30f3ea5c1960654623064ea","tid":285134,"uid":31531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T14:41:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a30c154889da1cb9b677bbde8f847ae00ecf9f9","tid":285134,"uid":43308,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T14:42:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"39066152dd0f384fc5142245b2926c0bf851c585","tid":285134,"uid":104684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:04:12.000Z","msg":"收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9b216c4583de51a7476ecb81044e1f27a0931f9","tid":285134,"uid":59268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-15T15:14:41.000Z","msg":"如果2個無工返無錢駛就真係有差距喇"},{"pid":"96c43ca191d76089b22090a297ffaa61d46a95e6","tid":285134,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T19:28:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}